---
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Acquisition quality vs. durable value — William Gieng</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500&family=Source+Serif+4:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-stone-50 font-sans text-stone-900 min-h-screen">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 py-5">

      <!-- Top bar -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-md px-5 py-3.5 mb-7">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 text-stone-900">
            <img src="/images/avatar.jpg" alt="William Gieng" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-sm leading-tight">William Gieng</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 leading-tight">Staff Data Scientist, Qualtrics</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-5 text-sm text-stone-500">
            <a href="/#work" class="text-stone-900">Work</a>
            <a href="/#writing">Writing</a>
            <a href="/#tools">Tools</a>
            <a href="/#notes">Notes</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
        <nav class="md:hidden flex gap-4 text-xs text-stone-500 mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-stone-100">
          <a href="/#work" class="text-stone-900">Work</a>
          <a href="/#writing">Writing</a>
          <a href="/#tools">Tools</a>
          <a href="/#notes">Notes</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <!-- Back link -->
      <a href="/#work" class="inline-block text-xs text-stone-500 mb-4">← Back to selected work</a>

      <!-- Case study header -->
      <article class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-8 md:p-10 mb-5">
        <div class="h-1 w-10 rounded-sm mb-5" style="background: #185FA5"></div>
        <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">01 — Retention</p>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium leading-tight mb-4 max-w-3xl">
          Acquisition quality vs. durable value: a multi-method retention diagnosis
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base text-stone-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          When a competitor disruption drove a 280K subscriber spike, was it real growth or borrowed users? Three independent lenses on the same question.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
          <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-blue-50 text-blue-900">Survival analysis</span>
          <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-blue-50 text-blue-900">Segmentation</span>
          <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-blue-50 text-blue-900">LLM VOC</span>
          <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-blue-50 text-blue-900">Predictive modeling</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Deck -->
      <section style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e7e5e4; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #78716c; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin: 0;">Full case study deck</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px;">
          <a href="/decks/retention-diagnosis.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="flex: 1; text-align: center; padding: 12px 20px; background: #1e293b; color: white; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;">Open deck in new tab ↗</a>
          <a href="/decks/retention-diagnosis.pdf" download style="flex: 1; text-align: center; padding: 12px 20px; background: white; color: #1e293b; border: 1px solid #e7e5e4; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;">Download PDF ↓</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer note -->
      <article class="bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-7">
        <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">Note</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
          All figures and data shown in the deck are synthetic and anonymized to preserve confidentiality. The analytical patterns and methodological framework reflect real work; specific numbers do not.
        </p>
      </article>

    </main>

    <style is:global>
      body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; }
      .font-serif { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif; }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>